                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-103-victim706 t18280110-103-viclabel531"></join>. The prisoner slept there on the 29th of December - another man slept in the same room: about a quarter-past eight o'clock in the morning, the prisoner got up, and asked me to let him out; he went away, and in a few minutes I missed the sheet; I ran and caught him, about a quarter of a mile off; he produced the sheet from under his smock-frock, and said he did it out of a joke.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
